Package: CNproScan
Title: CNproScan detects and annotates CNVs in bacterial genomes. 
Version: 0.0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Robin",
           family = "Jugas",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "robinjugas@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4675-0985"))
Description: CNproScan applies Generalized Extreme Studentized Deviate to detect outliers in the read-depth signal. 
  It also analyses BAM file for discovering read pairs mapping discordancies, which are used for CNV annotation. 
  See https://github.com/robinjugas/CNproScan
